conda/25.11.0:
   NOTE: We now recommend using micromamba instead to install and manage
   Conda environments. See the installation guide here: https://mamba.readthedocs.io/en/latest/installation/micromamba-installation.html#automatic-install
   In Slurm job scripts, micromamba can be enabled with the following: eval
   "$(micromamba shell hook --shell bash)" If you have any questions,
   contact carc-support@usc.edu.

